title: Walk-in Closets, Stainless Steel Appliances, 24-Hour Service Line
posting_body: ['Welcome To The Best of KentArterra’s apartments and townhomes are in a great location in the city of Kent, allowing residents to live a quiet life without being too far from the action.', 'Our two- and three-bedroom floor plans offer fireplaces, washer/dryers, walk-in closets, and private patios or decks.', 'Many have updated features such as stunning quartz countertops, faux wood flooring, and new cabinets.', 'As a resident, you can enjoy the clubhouse, brand-new playground, updated fitness center, business center, and a seasonal swimming pool.', 'Affordable living, a convenient location and great amenities make Arterra the perfect place to call home.', '-Stainless Steel Appliances', '-Wood-burning Fireplaces', '-Business Center', '-Walk-in Closets', '-Full Size Washer/Dryer', '-Fitness Center', '-Quartz Countertops', '-24-Hour Service Line', '-Pet Friendly', '-Clubhouse', '-Pool', '-Walking Distance To Shopping', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.']
